@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dpguxe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.51
    tmp = (wp.abs(v1) - ((v0 + 0.49 * tmp + 0.18) * (v1 + 0.99 - v0 + 0.33)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.57 * v2 + 0.83)) * tmp)
    tmp = v1
    tmp = ((v2 - (v2 + 0.79 + v2 + 0.96)) - wp.sin(v2))
    tmp = (0.78 / wp.exp((tmp + 0.46 - v2 + 0.54)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.17 + tmp + 0.61)) * (v2 + wp.abs(v0 + 0.32)))
    data[tid] = v0
